SwissRETS JSON Schema

Type: object

The SwissRETS inventory.

 No Additional Properties

root created
Type: stringFormat: date-time

Must be at least 1 characters long

root generator
Type: object
No Additional Properties

root generator name
Type: string

Must be at least 1 characters long

root generator version
Type: string

Must be at least 1 characters long

root projects

Project

Type: array
No Additional Items

Each item of this array must be:

root projects projectType
Type: object

Building project container.

 No Additional Properties

Type: string

root projects projects items referenceId
Type: string

root projects projects items seller organization email
Type: string

Very loose email like strings, validation basically just checks, if there is an @ sign and a dot after that.

 Must match regular expression: [^@]+@[^\.]+\..+

root projects projects items seller organization emailRem
Type: string

This field is depricated and will be removed in a future major version!

Same definition as email

root projects projects items seller organization phone
Type: string

Strings of at least three digits, may start with a plus sign and can have single spaces between digits, leading and trailing whitespace are not allowed.

 Must match regular expression: ^[+]?([0-9] )*[0-9]{3,}$

root projects projects items seller organization mobile
Type: string

Strings of at least three digits, may start with a plus sign and can have single spaces between digits, leading and trailing whitespace are not allowed.

Same definition as phone

The emailaddress dedicated for receiving inquiries and applications. This email address should not be presented publicly and is only intended as an indirect recipient using an online form or similar.

root projects projects items availability
Type: object

Mutually exclusive lifecycle state.

 No Additional Properties

root projects projects items availability state

AvailabilityState

Type: string

Lifecycle state of properties.

Must be one of:

  • "active"
  • "private"
  • "reference"
  • "reserved"
  • "taken"

root projects projects items availability start
Type: stringFormat: date-time

root projects projects items availability expiration
Type: stringFormat: date-time

root projects projects items constructionStatus

ConstructionStatusType

Type: enum (of string)

Construction status of project.

Must be one of:

  • "planned"
  • "under-construction"
  • "ready"
  • "completed"

Type: object

Price ranges for marketing purposes.

 No Additional Properties

root projects projects items prices currency
Type: string
Must match regular expression: ^[A-Z]{3}$

root projects projects items prices rent

projectPriceRent

Type: object

Recurring rental price.

 No Additional Properties

root projects projects items prices rent netFrom
Type: integer

Value must be greater or equal to 0

root projects projects items prices rent netTo
Type: integer

Value must be greater or equal to 0

root projects projects items prices rent interval

PriceIntervalType

Type: enum (of string)

The payment interval, the price stands for.

Must be one of:

  • "onetime"
  • "day"
  • "week"
  • "month"
  • "year"

root projects projects items prices rent referring

PriceReferringType

Type: enum (of string)

For what area the price stands for.

Must be one of:

  • "all"
  • "m2"
  • "km2"
